#

Carrot and Ginger Juice

10 min
$2.5
80 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeRaw

Cuisine:

Global

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

JuiceHealthyDetox

Description

A refreshing, vibrant juice that combines the natural sweetness of carrots with the zing of fresh ginger.

Ingredients

  • carrots: 4 medium
  • fresh ginger: 1 inch
  • water: 1 cup
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon (optional)
